val articles = spark
    .read
    .format("org.apache.spark.sql.cassandra")
    .options(Map("keyspace" -> "profiles", "table" -> "contentitems_uniqueid"))
    .load()
    .filter($"site" === lit("nunl"))
    .selectExpr("uniqueid AS id", "tags", "title", "topics")
    .filter(size($"tags") > lit(0))
    .select($"id", $"title", $"topics", explode($"tags").alias("tag"))
    .filter(!isEmptyMap($"topics"))

val titleJoined = spark.sql("""
    select user, readArticleTitle, title as recommendedTitle, maxScore from (
        select user, title as readArticleTitle, recommended as recommendedArticle, maxScore, normalizedScore
        from joinedReads
        join articles on substring(joinedReads.readArticle, 13 + 1) = articles.id -- 13 is length of "nunl:article:"
    ) as x
    join articles on x.recommended = articles.id
""")
titleJoined.write.mode(SaveMode.Overwrite).orc("s3://sanoma-smbene-bigdata-team/dsnl/dev/MDN-16037/titleJoined")
